    Scope and Contents
The Constitutional Convention 1973-74 and SSU Constitution 1975 files include: documents, memoranda and correspondence.  Included are drafts for Faculty Bill of Rights, Constitution, powers and responsibilities of the University Governance Structure.  Memoranda are from President Robert Spencer and convention members of the University Assembly.  This material contains the first constitution of this university. It defines membership in the university community, components of the Governance System, the university governance process and the realtionship netween governance and administration.  Material is arranged chronologically.  
  
